---
import DMVideo from "../../assets/images/DrumMixers/DMVideo.mp4";
import baghouse from '../../assets/images/DrumMixers/baghouse.png';
import baghouse2 from '../../assets/images/DrumMixers/baghouse2.png';
import Image from 'astro/components/Image.astro';
import SeparatorBlue from '../unitComponents/SeparatorBlue.astro';
---
<div class="w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-grisT font-bold mt-20 gap-6">
    <h1 class="w-full text-start px-8 lg:px-52 text-2xl md:text-4xl lg:mb-10">INTEGRATED BAGHOUSES</h1>
    <div class="w-full px-8 lg:px-52">
        <SeparatorBlue/>
    </div>
    <div class="px-8 lg:px-52">
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg">Baghouses are crucial for controlling dust and maintaining air 
            quality in industrial settings. They efficiently capture particulate matter, 
            ensuring compliance with environmental standards and creating a safer work environment. Ideal
             for industries like asphalt plants and aggregate processing, baghouses offer reliable, long-lasting performance.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 justify-center items-center gap-10 w-full">
        <div class="px-8 lg:pl-52 bg-white border-black border-2 md:rounded-r-2xl py-10">
            <h2 class="text-black text-xl md:text-2xl">Ranging from 4,000 to 90,000 ACFM Capacity</h2><br>
            <p>The baghouses are highly efficient at capturing fine particles,<span class="text-black"> achieving up
                 to 99.99% filtration</span>. Total and homogeneous return of fines to the hot-mix 
                 to optimize its quality and pavement life.</p><br>
            <p>Their advanced filtration system ensures cleaner air, 
                contributing to a greener, more eco-conscious workplace.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-8 lg:pr-52">
            <Image src={baghouse} alt="" class="w-3/4 xl:w-1/2"/>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full flex flex-col md:flex-row text-white my-10">
        <Image src={baghouse2} alt="" class="w-full h-auto md:h-[250px] object-cover"/>
        <div class="bg-blueMain px-4 md:px-8 lg:pr-52 py-6 lg:py-0 flex flex-col items-center justify-center md:rounded-l-2xl">
            <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-4">
                Mechanism of baghouses available in pulse jet and reverse jet
            </h2>
            <p class="text-grisSubP mb-4 md:mb-0">
                <span class="text-white">Pulse Jet:</span> A cleaning system that uses short bursts of compressed air to dislodge
                 dust and debris from the filter bags, maintaining continuous airflow and filtration efficiency.
            </p><br>
            <p class="text-grisSubP">
                <span class="text-white">Reverse Air:</span>
                A cleaning system that directs low-pressure air in the opposite direction to remove dust 
                from the filter bags, typically used in larger baghouses or high-dust 
                applications.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full flex justify-center items-center gap-10 px-8 md:px-52 bg-grisT py-10">
        <div>
            <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white">Different Types of Filter Bags and Their Specific Applications:</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-grisSubP">
                <li>Polyester</li>
                <li>Nomex</li>
                <li>Polyamide (P84)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full flex justify-center">
        <video src={DMVideo} autoplay playsinline muted loop class="w-3/4"></video>
    </div>
    
       
</div>